Package net.novazero.lib.ikbus

Contains the core abstractions for I/K-bus packets, messages, parsers, module descriptors and vehicle network profiles.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IKBusMessage
    Interface for classes that can represent I/K-bus messages.
    IKBusMessageParser
    Interface for classes that can parse I/K-bus messages from a packet.
    IKBusProfile
    Interface for classes that can provide an I/K-bus profile definition.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseIKBusMessage
    Abstract base class for objects that represent I/K-bus messages.
    BaseIKBusProfile
    Base implementation of an I/K-bus profile.
    CompoundIKBusMessageParser
    An I/K-bus message parser that is composed of a set of of other parsers.
    IKBusModuleDescriptionProvider
    Database that can provide module descriptors for I/K-bus modules based on their identifier/address.
    IKBusModuleDescriptor
    Class used for representing the static descriptions of I/K-bus modules.
    IKBusPacket
    Class for describing I/K-bus packets in their most basic form.
    IKBusUtils
    Class which holds generic I/K-bus utility methods.
    UnknownIKBusMessage
    Message used to encapsulate unrecognized I/K-bus messages which preserves the message contents.
    UnknownIKBusMessageCatcher
    I/K-bus message parser that serves as a fall-back in case its delegate parser is unable to parse a message.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    IKBusMessageParseException
    Exception that is thrown when an IKBusMessageParser encounters an error while parsing a message from a packet it recognizes.
    InvalidIKBusPacketException
    Exception that will be thrown when an array of bytes does not represent a valid I/K-bus packet.

Package net.novazero.lib.ikbus Description

Contains the core abstractions for I/K-bus packets, messages, parsers, module descriptors and vehicle network profiles.
